{"tid":1067820,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【霸氣盃】雲加：就如過往一樣 我將支持阿仙奴","createTime":"2019-03-18T20:14:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T07:20:36.000Z","uid":165817,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9328aed4f8b2464f6750d6b15f5fae154def4fbd","tid":1067820,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T20:14:15.000Z","msg":"前阿仙奴領隊雲加讚揚了安察洛堤，但他還是堅信拿玻里很難擊敗阿仙奴。<br />\n<br />\n拿玻里將在歐霸盃八強對陣阿仙奴，前者先客後主，兩回合賽事將分別在當地時間四月十一日和十八日進行。<br />\n<br />\n前阿仙奴主帥雲加表示：「就像過往其他比賽一樣，在阿仙奴與拿玻里的歐霸盃比賽中，我將支持阿仙奴，我亦不需要給艾馬利建議。<br />\n<br />\n同時，我也很欣賞安察洛堤，他是最佳的領隊之一，是團隊足球理念的大師。」<br />\n<br />\n「不過我還是要說，阿仙奴是一支偉大的球隊，拿玻里想要擊敗他們，將是非常困難的。」"},{"pid":"ce8c9d19a8d6a200e3999582fea333d9279bb536","tid":1067820,"uid":18276,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T20:20:30.000Z","msg":"爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a394b5830250c24023889d0cde50aaa14b0fae32","tid":1067820,"uid":154738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T00:31:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72097a54db3f9bf74f5692b0e3a8b3fd11378109","tid":1067820,"uid":56649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T00:39:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a64ccd8be3d0a2706bbd9a8a1916fa9987b4db","tid":1067820,"uid":41524,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T00:43:29.000Z","msg":"始終如一<br />\n我最敬重嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae73c97d97cf450174dc1bb13924d8b39487cfbe","tid":1067820,"uid":5549,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T00:45:22.000Z","msg":"雲加可否不要老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"143b9d10031457575e5cf63a03e9a3be2636eb78",